column5: We hit the ice down here in Pa. again at the promised land state park once again the chain pickeral didn't dissapoint along with some brookies and Lm bass thrown in for good measure. We also had an unexpected guest hanging around all day.
Nice to see an ice-fishing report from south of the border !!!   glad to see you caught a few !!!...cheers
Great report and pics Ranger22  Looks like you guys had a blast out there    WTG Leechman
